## KSPF Growth Plan & Strategy Roadmap

Build a clear, actionable growth roadmap for KSPF studio covering positioning, lead generation, revenue targets, and quarterly milestones. This issue tracks the work of turning the research report into an executable strategy.

**Research source:** [Growth Research Report (Google Doc)](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OC5QkGrn4n-VRczZ0Dz6eQJ3QH6iAFTiWvrwQrZkUI0/edit)  
**Strategy doc:** `ops/growth-strategy.md`

---

## Context

KSPF is a solo creative studio (Melbourne) in rebuild/growth mode. First active client (Alt Cosmetics) delivers ~20 March. Lead gen tools are built but pipeline not yet activated. No case studies published. No direct outreach started. Positioning and pricing not clearly defined externally.

The goal of this issue is to move from "tools built, plan sketched" → **pipeline running, proof of work published, revenue growing**.

---

## The Three Pillars

1. **Portfolio & Proof** — Publish case studies so outreach actually lands
2. **Pipeline** — Run systematic outreach (5 contacts/week from April)
3. **Revenue** — Diversify through Askable + retainers while project pipeline builds

